<div class="hero-header">
<h1><%= @title %></h1>
<% if @style == 'band' %>
<p class="lead">We are a Los Angeles-based live-music band and we sound a lot like this. Young Love is our first record and we made it ourselves. We are currently playing or booking shows all around California. Check here for dates. Want us to come to your town? Let us know!</p>

<% else %>

<p class="lead">Yoga every week. Find me at YAS in Silverlake, Los Angeles Boulders in DTLA, and Cliffs of Id in Culver City. Namaste!</p>

<% end %>

</div>

</div>

